      "notes": [
        "Page-specific helpers (custom-danger-alert/custom-alert-primary) still use raw hex (#d9272d, #0d60da).",
        "Backgrounds should map to color.*.50 tokens instead of hard-coded values for easier theming."
      ]
    },
